A financial information service that provides a real-time display of data from the [[MtGox]] exchange.

* Time Sales - Time price and volume for each trade executed
* Ticker - Current best ask / best bid, day's high, day's low, volume and last trade.
* Order Book - The buy (bid) and sell (ask) orders 

The Ticker and Time Sales services were announced on June 03, 2011 (1.1) and the Order Book was announced on June 10, 2011 (1.2).

